This will cause error when we use Gemini via openapi spec

```
org.springframework.ai.retry.NonTransientAiException: 400 - [{
  "error": {
    "code": 400,
    "message": "* GenerateContentRequest.tools[0].function_declarations[0].parameters.properties[toolContext].properties[context].properties: should be non-empty for OBJECT type\n",
    "status": "INVALID_ARGUMENT"
  }
}
]
```

I encounter error above after i use ToolContext, at then i found that the issue was due to inputSchema included the ToolContext as below

```
inputSchema={
  "$schema" : "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type" : "object",
  "properties" : {
    "pipelineName" : {
      "type" : "string"
    },
    "toolContext" : {
      "type" : "object",
      "properties" : {
        "context" : {
          "type" : "object"
        }
      },
      "required" : [ "context" ]
    }
  },
```
